                            latin: "Allāhumma innā laka ‘alayya huqūqan katsīratan fīmā bainī wa bainaka, wa huqūqan katsīran fīmā bainī wa baina khalqika. Allāhumma mā kāna laka minhā faghfirhu lī, wamā kāna likhalqika fatahammalhu ‘annī, wa aghninī bihalālila ‘an harāmika wa bithā’atika ‘an ma’shiyatika wa bifadhlika ‘amman siwāka yā wāsi’al maghfirati. Allāhumma inna baitaka ‘azhīmun, wa wajhaka karīmun, wa anta yā Allāhu, halīmun karīmun ‘azhīmun, tuhibbul ‘afwa fa’fu’annī.",
